{"title":"“黄松岭的火灾”（图片）","authors":["苏坚","马寻"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":6,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“黄松岭的火灾”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏坚画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马寻诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放洋的工友们望见了火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两步当一步的跑向楞场；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“救火啊！”他们在喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵景林打头当先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神色悲愤，万分紧张！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“糟了！”老赵心想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半天不见阎怪头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非是他放的火？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然，当他们奔至楞场挣扎起来的所长叫着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快抓阎怪头……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵景林立刻打发另两个工人去查找坏家伙……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天的大火啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧了一大垛木材；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又扑向另一垛木材！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——救啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——救啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民祖国的财产；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们劳动的血汗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老赵登上木垛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨动木材；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了危险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘了自个！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横在他心头的只有一个意志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有木材，他们就不得活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧得劈拍直响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰中奔跑着所长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他参加抢救，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着棍伤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凶暴的大火烧完了楞场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万棵原木归于灰烬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火势奔向林务所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们又开始拆毁木屋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火像匹万恶的野兽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔑视着人们所有的努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吼叫着扩张它的恐怖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二十三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林务所烧完了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大火又狂奔森林！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工友个个像上战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和敌人作殊死斗争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是人手少啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又被大火冲乱了阵营！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}